description: Jade Marx is one of the most sensual women I have ever seen. Having been a fan of hers for so long, I was thrilled to hear she was coming in for a shoot with Chanta. But when she got to the studio I couldn't help myself, I had to be the one who played with her. So, I nabbed her and we rode the elevator down to a different studio where no one would find us. And boy did we have fun. In fact, I had such a good time playing with her, I decided she was just too tasty to let go. I cleaned her up, scrubbed all the dirt and cum off of her, and left her there. Now I can have the beautiful Jade Marx anytime I want....stay tuned to see what happens next.
title: COLLECTION: PART 1
